# Roster Portraits

Drop first-party, rights-cleared roster portraits in this folder using these exact filenames:

## Owners

- `yuris-del-thumphouse-owner-hero.jpg`
- `charles-doyle-sr-thumphouse-owner-hero.jpg`

## Coaches

- `jorge-rubio-thumphouse-coach-hero.jpg`
- `loui-taylor-boxing-by-lou-hero.jpg`
- `osvaldo-tito-bourzac-thumphouse-mitts-hero.jpg`
- `oriol-martinez-miami-coach-hero.jpg`

## Fighters

- `neslan-machado-pitbull-hero.jpg`
- `yosdiel-napoles-miami-assassins-hero.jpg`
- `kevin-teddy-castillo-pro-boxer-hero.png`
- `charles-doyle-jr-playboy-charlie-hero.jpg`
